### Other Options

When publishing research data, please consider using[the data platform mdx (Data Platform for the Promotion of Data Utilization)](https://mdx.jp/)， For storing non-public computational results and similar data, you may also consider using [supercomputing systems](https://www.cc.u-tokyo.ac.jp/supercomputer/)In addition, you may consider individually subscribing to commercial cloud storage services such as Dropbox or Box.


